Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:23.33,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:29.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:38.40,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:45.24,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:54.06,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
