Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:00.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Sawachika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Sano from 2-A.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:05.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure you know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:08.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not seeing anybody yet, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So how’s about—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you like meat-potato stew or curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, meat-potato stew, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:18.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you thinking of cooking it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:22.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Never dream of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:27.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought if you wanted, we could go out…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:33.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doomed from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t hog her all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:43.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t reject a guy so coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.30,0:02:47.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Times like that, \Nhe’s like a peacock,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,ready to spread his wings\Nand jump off a roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:04.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someplace to go,\Nso I won’t be needing the car.
