Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Curry or meat-potato stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear guys prefer meat-potato stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:39.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(551,313)}Potatoes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.54,0:03:43.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they? I wouldn’t really know…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? “How do you make it?”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:49.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, first, you’ll need:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:54.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,round onions, potatoes, carrots, beef and stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:50.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(551,313)}Onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:51.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(551,313)}Potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:52.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(551,313)}Carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:53.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(551,313)}Beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’re you making this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.67,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\bord0\an4\fnDesertDogHmk\b1\c&H1A1C19&\pos(249,241)\frz22.595}5 potatoes\N\N1 carrot\N\N1 onion,\Nsugar, soy sauce\Nstock or sake\N\Nbeef round or\Nbelly pork\N\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:05.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about one for you, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I eat it right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:16.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange… I don’t see any red price tags\NTenma said to look out for…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:20.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight’s dinner is\NDaddy’s favorite, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:23.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure he’ll love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:23.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s cooking her first meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:45.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn’t Eri’s family have a cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:48.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn’t the cook fix\Nthe meat-potato stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:53.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, that wouldn’t show how Eri feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, Miko-chin?\NHow she feels about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You’re right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to get home\Nand take in the laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tsukamoto! You’ll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.79,0:05:07.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The butler, Nakamura,\Ntold me you were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, for dinner, I’m—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,About dinner…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve got to leave Japan on business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can’t have dinner with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don’t worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I made a date to have\Ndinner with my friends tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:08.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I know how busy you are,\Ntraveling all around the world and all…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame. We haven’t spent\Ntime with each other in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.91,0:06:14.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll come again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:16.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:20.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. ’Bye, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s not far, I can walk you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a short ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:17.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you like?\NMeat-potato stew or curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry.
