Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Sara-kun. ’Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:48.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Tsukamoto-kun around?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo said she was\Nstopping by the faculty office…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:53.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Thanks! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.89,0:08:06.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So then this guy goes…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:10.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:12.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that well-known?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.39,0:08:13.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,’Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:14.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Moderately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:27.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where Karasuma-kun is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:44.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the month, no money… Itoko won’t\Nlend me any. Not even lunch money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You skipped lunch, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:05.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do is fill your\Nempty stomach with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This always happens\Nat the end of the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:13.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I like you. The next time\NI get paid, I’ll treat you to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:22.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what do you like,\Ncurry or meat-potato stew?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:26.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I think we’re gonna get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Next time, I’ll treat you to curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.84,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Box lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:41.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I could get closer to him\Nif I made him a box lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.55,0:09:43.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t I think of it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:47.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is my time to shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curry? For school lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:58.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Curry! In Tupperware\Nwith rice and sauce. Two apiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:10:00.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um… Me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mildly spiced, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:58.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… um…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:06.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I made too much lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t you help me eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:13.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I’ll drink some water…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma sure seemed happy\Nwhen she went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With a big box lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it’s curry for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who’d make curry for a box lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:36.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:37.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Harima. I’m gonna settle\Nthe score once and for all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be waiting behind the gym after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:53.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Tenma-chan made\Ncurry that I love, and for two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she have made it for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what’s inside, Karasuma-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:03.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might be something you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.87,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice… both boxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:18.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A horrible mistake!
