Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:09.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure can’t stand Hanai-sempai, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:15.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your rejection instinct isn’t\Nthat strong against other boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:19.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Um… It’s not that\NI dislike him in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:24.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m just not comfortable\Naround boys, so I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:29.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So a really direct approach like\Nhis scares you away even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:31.28,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:37.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But now you have to go to 2-C,\Nyour sister and Hanai-sempai’s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:37.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The two boxes of curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry. I’ll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:46.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let’s hope that Hanai-sempai isn’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.89,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H111312&\fnTahoma\b1\fs80\clip(m 554 75 l 557 4 258 3 246 80)\move(582,72,578,70)}I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:57.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:13:59.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai-sempai is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:06.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Off I go! To see Tsukamoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.95,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H111312&\fnTahoma\b1\fs80\clip(m 554 75 l 557 4 258 3 246 80)\move(582,72,480,70,400,1960)}I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong, Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:15.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hanai! Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:16.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.12,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H111312&\fnTahoma\b1\fs80\clip(m 554 75 l 557 4 258 3 246 80)\move(480,70,595,70)}I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And you get this…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.93,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it? I’m going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:28.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what’s your hurry, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:31.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to see Tsukamoto-kun now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.93,Signs-opaq,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord5\fs26\c&H1A1C19&\b1\fnQuillScript\3c&H3A4184&\move(850,428,447,428,0,946)}Biggest Fool Over Yakumo In This Era
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:37.93,Signs-opaq,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\c&H1A1C19&\3c&HF0F2EF&\b1\fnQuillScript\move(850,428,447,428,0,946)}Biggest Fool Over Yakumo In This Era
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:41.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great! That girl’s so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:45.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like her, too. Leave her for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, hold it, hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just do it fast, and it’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:02.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yakumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.92,0:15:23.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yakumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, didn’t the box lunch\Ncause problems for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:47.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, time to leave for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don’t make me nag!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:53.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna skip school again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that’s\Nwhat delinquents do, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain’t going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:15.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can a tough street fighter\Nlike you be so weak inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.56,0:16:16.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain’t going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:20.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t trust guys or girls, so I ain’t going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:46.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Super’s Super Fun Science!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:48.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.01,0:16:50.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,On today’s Super Fun Science,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:53.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,we’re going to study optical illusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:57.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Problem #1! Look carefully at this picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Which line is longer: line number 1, or number 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s gotta be 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The correct answer is,\Nthey’re both the same length!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re kidding! You’re sure? Seems fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:10.16,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s measure it with this ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain’t 2 just a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:14.13,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,1 is this long. And 2 is… See? The same length!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called an optical illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:24.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Illusion, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.90,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx30\t(0,480,\fscx100)\fscy30\t(0,480,\fscy100)\fad(100,0)\bord3\c&H857CCD&\3c&HEBEAE3&\fnMushu\fs80\b1\move(332,335,331,436,0,480)}The Three Slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:43.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So… you’re going away? What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:44.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangoku-sama…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.49,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mangoku, don’t tell me you left
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:03.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,because you knew that the girl\Nwas in love with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:09.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense. You got it all wrong.\NThat girl wasn’t interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t put up a front like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.39,0:18:14.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew, didn’t you? Actually?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:17.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on! Right on, Mangoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:22.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I know the pain you’re suffering now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down and listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are actually siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:54.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then… Then you’re my… brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother and sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why we felt so close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:06.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You misunderstood, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that’s it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:10.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all an illusion and misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan and Karasuma are…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t it good, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is, Little Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re siblings!
