Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why we’re so close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:31.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? So that’s it!
