Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:39.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell the truth,\NI’ve always… loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.42,0:19:50.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I made a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:53.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji-kun, you’ve got company. What’ll I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:58.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it’s someone you know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s Ten—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a misunderstanding, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:03.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tennoji…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:18.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right. It was too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got your nerve,\Nskipping out on our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see you for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:50.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I so bad… at fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:20:59.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain’t no fun today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back if you wanna get even!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, are rice balls enough\Nfor lunch tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re fine, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:33.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima… Harima…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:37.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji Harima, are your tomorrows all gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end of your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:54.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:22:00.40,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:04.83,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:10.30,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.92,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.59,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:21.08,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.01,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:28.27,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.41,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.60,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:40.61,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.62,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:49.53,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.51,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:08.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma, you actually\Nprefer curry to rice balls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:11.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t I notice that sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.26,0:23:13.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll cook you some\Ndelicious curry this time!
